OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWestminster urged to extend
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FTroubles payment scheme    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK government has been urged to    
OL,6, extend the deadline for a Troubles     
OL,7, victims payment scheme.                
OL,9,FThe Troubles Permanent Disability      
OL,10,FPayment (TPDP) scheme is open for      
OL,11,Fapplicants until August 2026.          
OL,13,FIt offers payments to those who        
OL,14,Fsuffered physical or psychological     
OL,15,Finjuries in the Troubles in Northern   
OL,16,FIreland.                               
OL,18,FHowever, an element of the scheme - a  
OL,19,Fone-off, tax-free payment backdated to 
OL,20,F2014 - will soon close for applicants. 
